Waa! I hate being on late!

* Iron, unknowingly, recieved the transmission from Alpha.
< Hmm...>*

" Transmission recieved."

* The frequency then switched to the personal computer system located within 
the Maximal City.*

" Cyndro...give me information on an energy signature East of here."

* Iron looked over her shoulder at Whistler.*

" Go ahead and meet our guests. I'll catch up."

* Though she didn't like it, Iron would have to wait until she recieved more 
information before she dealt with the newcomers.
So, slowing her pace, she waited.*

................................

* Diana sat alone in the halls of the Maximal City.
Hay! Where did that big dragon go?! And Rion?*

" RION?!!!"

* Her tiny mews echoed through the city walls like a roar.*
